data.title: Majestyx Archives
data.text:
Dedicated to preserving, restoring, and maintaining score music for entertainment and media since 1997

PLEASE NOTE: What is listed here is MY PERSONAL COLLECTION of score music. As such, it is here for the reference of others to know what music is or has been available. Apparently some people think this is a "request" site. It is not. Please refrain from emailing me with messages such as "hey, can you upload (fill-in-the-blank) for me?" Those messages will be promptly deleted. Thanks for your understanding.

Last update: 15-May-2024
